00:02:56.548 --> 00:03:01.668
A man was stripped naked, his feet tied together with a rope.

00:03:02.408 --> 00:03:08.228
The rope was tied to 5 horses, which dragged the man 6

00:03:08.368 --> 00:03:11.758
kilometres through the hard, cobbled streets of London.

00:03:12.898 --> 00:03:18.598
As he was being dragged along the streets, his head bumping up and down on the hard

00:03:18.608 --> 00:03:25.158
stones, crowds of people shouted at him, throwing stones and rotten vegetables.

00:03:26.058 --> 00:03:31.226
When he arrived at his final destination, an area of the city called Smithfield,

00:03:31.698 --> 00:03:37.678
the rope was cut, and the half-conscious man was dragged up onto a stage.

00:03:38.508 --> 00:03:46.058
From there, a rope was tied around his neck, he was pulled up, and hung until he was half dead.

00:03:46.818 --> 00:03:53.058
But instead of being left there to die, he was cut down, and placed on a table.

00:03:53.847 --> 00:04:00.567
